host_about: We are exotic fruit farmers, our main crop is Dragonfruit.   We love to travel and do so extensively. We love hosting people who understand that AirBnB is not a corporate hotel situation- but rather there are faces behind the hosting team who genuinely care about the experiences we give our guests.    If you are our guest and need something, call, we will help you any way we can.  Even though we may not get to meet you, we do care and want you to have a great experience. host_about:
Welcome to our Airbnb!

I'm Luna, and I'm excited to be your host during your stay in California. I'm passionate about good food, travel, and adventure, and I love sharing those experiences with others.

My small family and I have made California our home, and we love spending our free time exploring all that this place has to offer. From paddleboarding and watching the sunset to trying new restaurants and biking in different neighborhoods, we're always on the go. And when we want to relax, we love to make bonfires on the beach and enjoy picnics.

As your host, we want to ensure that your stay is as enjoyable and comfortable as possible. We know that the place you stay can make or break your travel experience, and we take that responsibility seriously. So please don't hesitate to let us know if there's anything we can do to make your time here better.

We truly enjoy connecting with new people and sharing stories, and we hope that your stay with us will be memorable in all the right ways!

Good to see you here on Airbnb!
